definitions.title: Def
definitions.body: [[גבב]] (prob. be curved, convex, elevated, Aram. [[גִּבְּבָא]] hill; be or make hollow, dig, Ar. jab=un cut off or out, jub=un, Aram. [[גּׁב]], Eth. gb: As. gubbu,—all = cistern; cf. e.g. As. gubbâni ša mê, cisterns of water, Asrb:Annals Col. viii. 102, KB:ii. 220; v. n.pr. [[גּׁב]] infr.)
